      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，TelemetryStream到PLC_Logic是单向数据流。PLC判断之后应该分支吧？Yes和No两条路径？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic"
